        Teacher object stores teacher information for scheduling.
        Parameters:
        id - id of the Student
        name - First and last name of a Teacher
        returningStudent - First and last name of the returning student of a Teacher.
        returningInstrument - The returning instrument of a Teacher.
        keepReturningStudent - Whether a Teacher wants to keep their returning student.
        instruments - String[] of instruments the Teacher can teach.
        instrumentExperience - String[] of instrument experience of a Teacher.
        genderPreference - Student gender preference of a Teacher.
        agePreference - Student age preference of a Teacher.
        levelPreference - Student level preference of a Teacher.
        languages - String[] of languages other than English a Teacher can speak.
        crimeRecord - Whether a Teacher has a crime record.
        availableTimes - String[] of available times a Teacher can teach.
